# Xcode — pure per-user IDE state (open tabs, window position), never project-relevant.
# Scheme files under xcuserdata/ are intentionally still tracked (see retry-sample/iosApp/README.md
# — the checked-in .xcodeproj is meant to open and run without any manual Xcode setup).
UserInterfaceState.xcuserstate

# Explicitly keep critical project meta
!LICENSE
!.github/

# Secrets and local configurations
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# JVM Crash Logs
hs_err_pid*.log
replay_pid*.log

# AI agent instruction files (local dev aid only, not shipped project docs)
AGENTS.md
